This paper deals with biomedical image segmentation using deep learning techniques. The paper discusses the use of multi-atlas segmentation and supervised learning-based segmentation strategies, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. The paper also focuses on medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and neural networks (cs.NE) which are relevant sub-categories for this work.
